title: [Ta'Illistim, Sylvar Wey]
description: A stately mansion stands far back from the intersecting streets, its yard immaculately landscaped and surrounded by a low-stacked stone fence.  Sweetly fragrant honeysuckle vines grow along the fence at regular intervals, their tiny yellow blooms nodding in the night's breeze.
